name: Charcoal Passive Amplifier
description:
Incredibly durable, renewable, and rich in tonal variation, bamboo and rattan bring a relaxed style to any area. Our passive amplifier is hand-made to create a unique and one of a kind look.
 
Frame is expertly crafted of Woven Bamboo and Rattan.

Phone Compatibility
 Small: iPhone
 Large: Galaxy SIII, SIV Galaxy 
Weight: 
 Small: .55 lb / .25 kg 
 Large: .60 lb / .27 kg 

For Daily Care, simply Wipe clean using a soft , dry cloth. To protect the finish, avoid the use of abrasive chemicals, harsh cleaners and rough cleaning pads and polishes. To remove lodged debris, we recommend using a vacuum with a brush attachment.
